        <title>Introduction to MERN stack</title>
    <h1>Welcome to the MERN Stack</h1>
    <p>MERN is a pre-built technology stack based on JavaScript technologies . MERN stands for MongoDB, Express, React, and Node, after the four key technologies that make up the stack. MongoDB — document database. Express(.js) — Node.js web framework. React(.js) — a client-side JavaScript framework.</p>
    <ol>
        <li>MongoDB</li>
        <li>Express.js</li>
        <li>React.js</li>
        <li>Node.js</li>
    </ol>
